2026-05-10T04:22:14.2153141Z 13    <!--
2026-05-10T04:22:14.2153717Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-10T04:22:14.2154594Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-10T04:22:14.2155776Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-10T04:22:14.2156924Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-10T04:22:14.2157938Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-10T04:22:14.2158707Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-10T04:22:14.2159267Z 20    -->
2026-05-10T04:22:14.2159889Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
